{"word":"H6131 - עָקַר - ʻâqar - aw-kar' - Dig down","slug":"H6131","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עָקַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻâqar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-kar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Dig down"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05E7;&#x05E8; - &#x201B;a&#x0302;qar</b> - <i>aw-kar'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>pluck</i> up (especially by the roots); specifically to <i>hamstring</i>; figuratively to <i>exterminate: - </i>dig down, hough, pluck up, root up."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6133\">H6133</a>, <a href=\"#/H6134\">H6134</a>, <a href=\"#/H6135\">H6135</a>, <a href=\"#/H6137\">H6137</a>, <a href=\"#/H6138\">H6138</a>, <a href=\"#/H6139\">H6139</a>"}]}